The food we had was delicious and far exceeded our expectations , since this was low priced.
They start you off with a complimentary cup of egg flower soup or a small fresh salad with peanut dressing.
We had Hot and Spicy Cashew Chicken and the Ginger Chicken Lunch Plates ($5.50@) Both were fresh and flavorful with a good meat to vegetable ratio and came with crispy vegetable roll and steamed rice shaped like a heart on your plate.
Besides YUMMY FOOD service was very good and We were HAPPY we stopped here !

